  "body": "<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/c3c067be7a67e093.jpg?v=1782796585\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>The studio is coming together slowly but surely. My main goal has been to set up \"stations\" so I am not the only one who knows where everything is. Adrienne with <a href=\"http://allreadymemories.bigcartel.com/\">All Ready Memories</a> has been a creative consulting client of mine for quite some time. As much as I love advising her on strategies for growing her business, I am a really big fan of her ideas and products.  As you probably already know, I have been organizing my washi tapes with their holders and think their washi wheels are genius. So when they came out with their newest innovative product, she sent one to me just in time to give my stamp pads a proper home.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"17b-.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/dce009c9a2f4da88.jpg?v=1782796588\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"17c-.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/87229bb49e00fc35.jpg?v=1782796591\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"17d-DSC_0186.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/a560f62d2fc4a086.jpg?v=1782796593\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"17e-DSC_0189.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/7b9a5beb779bc77d.jpg?v=1782796596\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"17f-DSC_0190.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/c73f00c65a58719b.jpg?v=1782796599\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>More Ideas Than Time Book <a href=\"http://sodalicious.pl/index.php\">by Sodalicious</a></p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/432b1f2a47a5094a.jpg?v=1782796602\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Hope to share more progress on the studio with you soon. I also asked Adrienne if she wanted to say anything for this sponsor spotlight, and she did! <em>Hello!  My name is Adrianne McQuitty and I own and operate All Ready Memories with my family in Noblesville, IN.  We operate out of my home office and my Dad’s (Jeff) workshop in my parent’s basement.  Every item is handmade, by us, with a focus on quality and functionality.  It all started because I desperately needed storage solutions for my ever growing stash of supplies and shrinking workspace!  So, I took these supplies to my Dad and we got to work developing ideas for products that would allow me to keep my favorite supplies close at hand without taking up a ton of space!  I find that if my stash is out of sight, it’s out of mind and never gets used, so we had to get creative!  And boy did my Dad get creative!  He had never heard of washi tape, yet was the brainchild and creator of our SUPER popular Washi Wheel…I love it so much!  </em></p><p><em>We’ve had so much fun on this new adventure and have met so many amazing people (including the fabulous Amy Tan!!) from all over the world!  I love how the crafting community supports each other and the inspiration &amp; talent is endless!  We hope you’ll stop by and check out </em><a href=\"http://allreadymemories.bigcartel.com/\"><em>our shop</em></a><em> and </em><em>blog</em><em> for new products, inspiration and organization solutions!  We have a lot of exciting stuff in store and we hope you’ll join in the fun!  Happy crafting!</em></p><p>Hope you all enjoyed this and continue to support small businesses. <a href=\"http://allreadymemories.bigcartel.com/\">All Ready Memories</a> wants to help you get organized as well and is offering 10% off your entire order. Use the code: ORGANIZE2014</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>"
}